922
01:07:36,588 --> 01:07:41,101
Karena liburan musim dingin dimulai,
di sini akan berisik anak-anak.

923
01:07:41,427 --> 01:07:44,429
Berpikir memasak tiga hidangan sehari

924
01:07:44,430 --> 01:07:46,639
- membuatku merinding.
- Setuju.

925
01:07:46,640 --> 01:07:48,224
- Ibu.
- Ibu.

926
01:07:48,225 --> 01:07:50,643
- Mereka datang.
- Halo.

927
01:07:50,644 --> 01:07:52,103
- Hai.
- Ibu.

928
01:07:52,104 --> 01:07:56,274
Sebelum kembali ke rumah,

929
01:07:56,275 --> 01:07:58,234
tunjukkan hasil ujian kalian.

930
01:07:58,235 --> 01:08:00,319
Kalian ikuti ujian akhir, 'kan?

931
01:08:00,320 --> 01:08:03,290
- Benar.
- Aku dapat nilai bagus.

932
01:08:05,993 --> 01:08:07,669
Begitu. Bagus.

933
01:08:08,370 --> 01:08:11,205
Aku hanya salah beberapa.

934
01:08:11,206 --> 01:08:12,457
Sungguh? Biar ibu lihat.

935
01:08:12,458 --> 01:08:15,001
Biar ibu lihat. Baiklah.

936
01:08:15,002 --> 01:08:17,003
Astaga, kau akan sukses dalam hidup!

937
01:08:17,004 --> 01:08:18,629
Kau bisa segalanya!

938
01:08:18,630 --> 01:08:19,890
Bagus!

939
01:08:21,467 --> 01:08:23,310
Ho Yeong, biar ibu lihat.

940
01:08:26,054 --> 01:08:27,314
Ibu.

941
01:08:27,764 --> 01:08:29,932
Ibu akan sangat malu.

942
01:08:29,933 --> 01:08:30,933
Tak apa-apa?

943
01:08:30,934 --> 01:08:33,153
Dasar berandal.

944
01:08:33,979 --> 01:08:36,022
Kenapa peringkat terakhir lagi?

945
01:08:36,023 --> 01:08:37,899
Dasar berandal!

946
01:08:37,900 --> 01:08:39,484
Wol Suk.

947
01:08:39,485 --> 01:08:42,778
